{"tid":2244542,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「兇版潤娥」親自下廚　身材辣翻…白皙豪乳快撐爆背心","createTime":"2020-10-15T14:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T10:27:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":23,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b9e59e6f49a501710e3d1024ed2b5fe1152097","tid":2244542,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"近年來，南韓出現許多長相姣好、身材傲人的女神DJ，在社群平台上獲得大批粉絲關注，而有著「兇版潤娥」封號的DJ MIU就是其中的代表。近期DJ MIU就分享了兩張下廚美照，展現性感身材。<br />\n<br />\n個人IG擁有超過130萬粉絲追蹤的DJ MIU，除了DJ本業之外，也當起YouTuber，讓粉絲們看到各式各樣的風格。近期，DJ MIU拍攝一系列的下廚影片，她也分享兩張美圖上傳IG，給粉絲們「聞香」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/15/2828746-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F15%2F2828746-PH.jpg&h=4b94a824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲DJ MIU下廚美圖。（圖／翻攝自2km2km IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/15/2828747-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F15%2F2828747-PH.jpg&h=8a1a77e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片中，DJ MIU以廚房為背景，鍋子旁還放著調味罐。她則是在流理台上切小番茄，身上穿著白色背心配上緊身牛仔褲，傲人上圍幾乎撐爆白色背心，完美胸型一覽無遺，展現性感的同時也讓人敬佩她穿搭的技巧。<br />\n<br />\nDJ MIU則在文中寫下，這是朋友的喬遷日，相關的烹飪與活動過程，都可以到YouTube上看。大批粉絲看完紛紛留言直呼性感，也有粉絲稱讚她是「最美DJ」。"},{"pid":"bb9ae1b5bf8f98e346fdefc2b299c2fe91ca21aa","tid":2244542,"uid":16659,"like":29,"dislike":15,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/15/2828749-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F15%2F2828749-PH.jpg&h=d86c5ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲DJ MIU下廚美圖。（圖／翻攝自2km2km IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/15/2610387-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F2610387-PH.jpg&h=a48d6243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲DJ MIU下廚美圖。（圖／翻攝自2km2